{"tid":179401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網友係淫魔    15歲女生應約見面慘遭刀脅非禮","createTime":"2017-03-30T08:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T01:17:51.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"510970c3d9aecb35c3fdc99954ac4e269cf77a11","tid":179401,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170330/large/1490853720_bf06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170330%2Flarge%2F1490853720_bf06.jpg&h=0b132394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170330/large/1490852528_85a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170330%2Flarge%2F1490852528_85a3.jpg&h=b2053343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【16:00更新】現場消息稱，女生與被捕男子在網上相識不久，今晨應約到對方禾輋邨寓所，未料卻遭人以利刀威嚇及非禮。<br />\n【13:40更新】警員搜捕3小時後，拘捕一名涉案的24歲男子<br />\n<br />\n早上10時許，年約15歲穿校服裙的女生向途人求助，指在沙田禾輋邨泰和樓樓上一單位，遭一名男子持刀指嚇及非禮。警員趕至現場，發現女生臉、兩手掌遭鎅傷，涉案色魔則逃往泰和樓平台，大批警員趕至搜捕。女生由女警陪同下送院敷治，案件暫列非禮及刑事恐嚇案。<br />\n其間特遣隊人員接報加入搜捕，約3小時後、即下午1時許，在泰和樓地下公園發現疑與案有關的男子，將他拘捕，稍後該男子被警員帶返泰和樓樓上單位調查，逗留約1小時後被帶往警署，探員同時撿走一袋證物。據悉，女生與被捕男子在網上相識不久，女生今晨應約到該男網友禾輋邨寓所，未料遭人以利刀威嚇及非禮，她反抗時遭鎅傷臉頸及雙手，最後負傷掙脫逃出單位求助。"},{"pid":"4a39ad5ff0a1a8eb1f9a765f6f0103c8c7624bef","tid":179401,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"15歲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">臉</span>、兩手掌遭鎅傷<br />\n<br />\nmola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90163c241e48d23e7eb1af43971ab32be271a7c6","tid":179401,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>女生與被捕男子在網上相識不久，今晨應約到對方禾輋邨寓所</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n直接結案唔洗查 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a6ce25add452eb82f2a676f32d8d5ab43dbd3","tid":179401,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">女生今晨應約到該男網友禾輋邨寓所</span><br />\n<br />\n佢父母無同佢講要保護好自己？上人屋企咁大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85603ef90688f6f1067f066ac329b145e39a312f","tid":179401,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"15歲今朝唔返學去見網友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91170b4a02d017f460d65745be9d053d3f36d24b","tid":179401,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"十五歲都咁on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2237c1279efb813dfd8e6d08f04ea5c499c8e31","tid":179401,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"103d5da917b53643b36dadf0e70bcc03c04b7d2d","tid":179401,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49f8cf0949201ca0eb019f42eba63d624d6551e5","tid":179401,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncc女做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遇著變態廢青<br />\n<br />\n🤷&zwj;♂️🤷&zwj;♂️🤷&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"fdbe387814c98e9b01169b74dff8cd15ba30ad20","tid":179401,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:51:20.000Z","msg":"估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e2a211e66147155e5cb27e6f837803bf6948b8","tid":179401,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime